<DATE_TIME> 1998-03-18 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> French Formula One Grand Prix Back on Calendar </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, March 18 (Xinhua) -- The French Formula One Grand Prix
is back on this season's calendar, announced the sports ruling
body FIA on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
FIA had removed the race out of this year's programme because
of a long simmering dispute over television rights.
</P>
<P>
Under French law it had been illegal for sporting events to be
sold exclusively to one channel. But last month the French
parliament adopted a new sports bill allowing sporting
organisations to sell exclusive rights.
</P>
<P>
This year's French Formula One Grand Prix will be held on June
28. 
</P>
</TEXT>
