-- Facing Israel, Europe has only two choices -- bow or crack.
The British Foreign Secretary Robin Cook's visit to Jerusalem on
Tuesday, which stirred a diplomatic incident and receiving an
unprecedented slap on the face from Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin
Netanyahu, fully showed that. 
