the season and he can do anything he wants to do.
</P>
<P>
Drexler, 35, leads Rocket scorers with 18.6 points, 5.5 assists
and 4.8 rebounds per game with a 43 percent shooting percentage.
</P>
<P>
His departure was surely to be a big blow to the Rockets that
stand seventh in the Western Conference after winning the NBA
titles in 1994 and 1995 when Michael Jordan attempted his baseball
ventures. 
