<HEADLINE> Italy, Ukraine Shores Up Military Cooperation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, March 17 (Xinhua) -- Italy and Ukraine reached here
Tuesday an accord on military cooperation ranging from training of
staff to acquisition of weaponry and technology.
</P>
<P>
Signed by Italian Defense Minister Beniam Andreatta and his
