important factor in attracting more investment and new investors,
said a provincial official.
</P>
<P>
The agricultural and industrial output volume of Hebei's
foreign-funded enterprises reached 52 billion yuan, up 21 percent
on an annual basis, with annual sales income in 1997 of 61.3
billion yuan, up 32 percent over the previous year. 
