<HEADLINE> Lazio Grabs UEFA Semifinal Berth </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, March 17 (Xinhua) -- Lazio of Italy entered the UEFA Cup
semifinals for the first time after drawing 2-2 with AJ Auxerre of
France in the second leg of the quarter-finals in Auxerre, France.
</P>
<P>
The tie meant that Lazio advanced with a 3-2 victory on
aggregate after Lazio won 1-0 in the first leg at home.
</P>
