on a pass from Czech midfielder Pavel Nedved.
</P>
<P>
Auxerre pulled one back six minutes before the break on striker
Stephane Guivarc'h, who converted a free kick.
</P>
<P>
Guivarc'h scored again 10 minutes from time with a header but
Auxerre could no longer beat the Lazio defence in the remaining
time. 
